{
  "texts": [
    "To identify suitable topics for our analysis, we divide the dataset by year and by country and run BERTopic algorithm on each subset.",
    "The results reported in Fig 1 show the most debated topics for each year by country and source category.",
    "The size of each topic represents the number of news sources contributing to it, while its position reflects its relevance to the overarching topics.",
    "The flow diagrams show the topic's prevalence in news outlets over time.",
    "In particular, the flow connecting two topics illustrates the evolving focus of news sources over time."
  ]
}